### Get all inventory items
GET https://localhost:7090/api/inventory

### Get a specific inventory item by ID
GET https://localhost:7090/api/inventory/1

### Add a new inventory item
POST https://localhost:7090/api/inventory
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "New Item",
  "description": "A brand new item",
  "quantity": 100,
  "price": 29.99
}

### Update the quantity of an inventory item
PUT https://localhost:7090/api/inventory/1/quantity
Content-Type: application/json

10


### Delete an inventory item
DELETE https://localhost:7090/api/inventory/2